      <p>Commercial reach-in refrigerators are workhorses in any restaurant kitchen. When they fail, the impact goes beyond the repair cost—you lose perishable inventory, food safety compliance is at risk, and kitchen workflow breaks down. Here is what owners actually pay for repair and replacement, and how to fund the fix fast.</p>
